\v 41 ∆Ч Yesu ma b'u ake mog re ita kemag…®nd Yerusalem taun wa menon yokatenenonda Ju r…®ga waina Uj ∆Чgwanti Nony Iyena Diyamdiyam W…®n…®nd.
