\p 
\v 1-2 ∆Ч God…®mna bage y…®t ikonj Jakariyamna b'…®ga Yoan…®m p…®lwa wul kesa tungg…®nd ongg…®t w…®n nat re piptin…®m (15) kemag rau Tiberiyom yet re Roma mopyam king Kaisamna p…®pmet…®nd y…®bnonj, …® kwa re Pontiyo Pilato Roma gabmani mopyam yeb…®m Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Erod king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Galili eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Erod…®mna y…®pa mog ke nany Pilip king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Ituraya eriya d…®de Trokoniti eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Lisaniyo king p…®pmet…®nd yeb…®m Abilene eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® kwa re Ana d…®de Kayapa y…®na mopyam s…® r…®ga p…®pmet…®nd rebna.
