\v 12 Aj…® Yesu tin m…®ra yomnonj da, вАЬY…®na peband kwa …®ja emb j…® yindeny da, вАШMan goro moina Yonggyam God…®nd otonkena m…®lend oramiten…®m!вАЩвАЭ
\v 13 ∆Ч re ket Satana ongg…®tyam komkesa otonkena m…®le undwasinonj, ton ket Yesund y…®raronj, ng…®rpu rokate ra kwa y…®pa b'og…®l w…®n okas otonkenam.
\v 14 ∆Ч ket Yesu Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngamna danda k…®ma na …®tendonj Galili eriya wa, s…® Ti gatab y…®d…®r y…®t re kea kupka eriya nata yikenonj.
\v 15 ∆Ч Ton kea r…®ga ouyaena eyeninonj towaina y…®r opmitenapu met nata, …® kea ket komkesa r…®gap Tin daka esourena yiyeno.
\s1 R…®gap Yesund Y…®sayo Najaret Taun…®nd
\r (Mat 13:53-58; Mak 6:1-6)
\p 
\v 16 ∆Ч ket Yesu …®tendonj Najaret taun wa r…®k…®nd re Ton ukoi awonj. ∆Ч re Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r awonj, Ton kea ket yikonj Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met wa Tina get ke m…®le r…®r…®r…®nd, d…®de ket b'…®garonj w…®ng…®r wa, …® ket onyitonj y…®na peba ogenkam.
\v 17 S…® re y…®na peba owama r…®gat Ti yokawonj bageyam Isayamna eoromki peba, Ton ket peba yobgokonj d…®de oraka yiyonj ongg…®tyam p…®pmet r…®k…®nd re odede y…®tkak …®r…®ki yeb…®m da,
\q1 
\v 18 вАЬYonggyam God…®mna W…®ngaw…®nga …®ta kor p…®l…®nd,
\q2 mop nok…®p Ton kea ken gaya ke neaukonj
\q1 Tina b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnenam gasa kesa r…®ga wa p…®lwa,
\q2 …® Ton kea ken n…®tm…®kitonj p…®tap…®ta omnenam Tina m…®le,
\q1 opi re da …®job…®ki r…®ga …®tr…®ngkam …® y…®rd…®d…® r…®ga y…®r …®pangkam,
\q2 …® d…®de beb…®g aw…®r omnam towa p…®lke yepim re beb…®g w…®rand wekeny,
\q1 
\v 19 …® kwa p…®tap…®ta omnenam ongg…®tyam kemag r…®denasim ra Yonggyam r…®ga kear tamneniny.вАЭ
