\v 37 S…® re komkesa r…®ga bobo yepiya re Gerasen eriya ke tuwonj, utkundeno towaina y…®t, ton kea Yesund danda k…®ma y…®gekeno towa p…®lke ewaikitam, mop nok…®p ton ukoi moga na auk…®to. S…® ket Yesu g…®ga wa angitonj d…®de ket yiwatonj.
