\v 15 Aj…® ongg…®t ten (10) r…®ga wa w…®ng…®r…®nd, re y…®pa r…®gat ton b'…®sakendi y…®r b'angonj, ton ket God…®nd ma sobijog na auwam k…®ma esourena yiyonj, ng…®rpu ket …®tendonj Yesum p…®lwa.
