\p 
\v 15 ∆Ч ket r…®gap towaina papa b'…®ga daka Yesum p…®lwa eyento odede nony k…®ma da Yesu ten tasopainy b'og…®l omnam. ∆Ч re Tina b'auyaena r…®gap ongg…®tyam m…®le y…®r yongo, ton kea ket ten samany k…®ma r…®ga ogoka eyento b'…®ga iyenam Yesum p…®lwa.
